WEBVTT

00:01.626 --> 00:06.464
♪ (HBO INTRO PLAYS) ♪

00:06.464 --> 00:09.217
♪ (SINGER SINGING
"ARE YOU MAKIN' ANY MONEY?"
BY CHICK BULLOCK) ♪

00:09.217 --> 00:13.763
<i>♪ You make time
And you make love dandy ♪</i>

00:13.763 --> 00:20.770
<i>♪ You make
Swell molasses candy ♪</i>

00:22.188 --> 00:24.566
<i>♪ But, honey
Are you making any money? ♪</i>

00:24.566 --> 00:27.277
<i>♪ That's all I want to know ♪</i>

00:27.277 --> 00:30.071
<i>♪ You make fun
And you could make trouble ♪</i>

00:30.071 --> 00:32.824
<i>♪ You make mistakes
And that goes double ♪</i>

00:32.824 --> 00:35.034
<i>♪ But, honey
Are you making any money? ♪</i>

00:35.034 --> 00:37.871
<i>♪ That's all I want to know ♪</i>

00:37.871 --> 00:40.248
<i>♪ You make dates
And you make trains ♪</i>

00:40.248 --> 00:44.335
<i>♪ I can get that through my head
It's a cinch, in a pinch ♪</i>

00:44.335 --> 00:48.131
<i>♪ You could make breakfast
Even make the bed ♪</i>

00:48.131 --> 00:51.342
<i>♪ Oh, you make good
When you make a promise ♪</i>

00:51.342 --> 00:54.053
<i>♪ No, I'm not
A doubting Thomas ♪</i>

00:54.053 --> 00:56.181
<i>♪ But, honey
Are you making any money? ♪</i>

00:56.181 --> 00:58.641
<i>♪ That's all I want to know ♪</i>

00:58.641 --> 01:04.397
- ♪ (MUSIC CONTINUES) ♪
